## What Was Built

### 🎨 Design System
- Deep navy/black dark theme with **indigo–violet–cyan** gradient palette
- `Outfit` + `Space Grotesk` Google Fonts
- Glassmorphism cards with blur + translucent borders

### 🌌 Three.js Scene (Hero)
- **2,800 colored star particles** slowly rotating in 3D space
- **Rotating wireframe icosahedron** with two orbiting torus rings
- Camera reacts to **mouse parallax** and **scroll offset**

### 📜 GSAP ScrollTrigger Animations
- `reveal-up`, `reveal-left`, `reveal-right` — staggered on every section
- Stat card counters animate to target number on scroll into view
- Active nav link highlight updates on scroll position

### 🏢 Six Companies Carousel
- Touch drag + button navigation + auto-play (every 4s)
- Each card has a per-mouse-position **3D tilt** effect
- Colored glow blobs unique to each company

### 🗺️ World Map Canvas
- Animated dot grid representing continents with pulsing highlights
- Bezier arc connection lines between global HQ hubs
- Region color-coded by geography

### ✅ Verified
All sections rendered correctly with no console errors.
